<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV91">
<l>paṇṇulāvu meṉmoḻippa ṭaittaṭaṅka ṇāḷporuṭ</l>
<l>ṭeṇṇilāva rakkaraine ruppiṉālne rukkiṉāy</l>
<l>kaṇṇalālor kaṇṇilēṉka lantacuṟṟam maṟṟilē</l>
<l>ṉeṇṇilāta māyaniṉṉai yeṉṉuḷnīkka leṉṟumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who crushed countless Rakshasas with fire[-like arrows]</l>
<l>For the sake of the Lady with a soft, melodious speech and large, weapon[-like] eyes!</l>
<l>I do not have any protection other than [yours], I do not have other close relatives.</l>
<l>O [Lord] with innumerable wonders! Don’t ever remove Yourself from my heart!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
